    <section class="service-section">
        <!-- ================= SERVICE AREAS HEADER ================= -->
        <section class="service-hero">
            <h2>SERVICES</h2>
            <p>
                Empowering communities through culture, education and opportunity. Join us as we create lasting change,
                one initiative at a time.<br><br> Together, we strive to uplift lives and preserve heritage through innovative,
                community-driven solutions
            </p>
            <br />
            <a href="#" class="btn-primary">LEARN MORE</a>
        </section>

        <h3>Key Service Areas</h3>

        <!-- ================= BLOCK 1 → PRIMARY HEALTHCARE ================= -->
        <article class="service-card">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/primary-health.jpg" alt="Primary Healthcare">
            <div class="card-body-left">
                <h4>Primary Healthcare</h4>
                <p>Lungisa offers primary healthcare services delivered by professional nurses. These services include:</p>
                <br />
                <ul>
                    <li>Management of minor ailments</li>
                    <li>Baby vaccinations</li>
                    <li>Management of chronic conditions</li>
                    <li>Family planning</li>
                    <li>HIV prevention, awareness, counselling, and testing facilitated by peer educators and HIV counsellors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- ================= BLOCK 2 → PSYCHOSOCIAL SUPPORT ================= -->
        <article class="service-card">
            <div class="card-body-right">
                <h4>Psychosocial Support</h4>
                <p>Lungisa's qualified social workers provide vital psychosocial therapy to:</p>
                <p><strong>Individuals • Families • Couples • Groups</strong></p>
                <br />
                <p>This comprehensive approach addresses a wide range of social problems, and the organization provides referrals when specialised care is necessary.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/psychosocial.jpg" alt="Psychosocial Support">
        </article>

        <!-- ================= BLOCK 3 → YOUTH DEVELOPMENT ================= -->
        <article class="service-card">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/primary-health.jpg" alt="Primary Healthcare">
            <div class="card-body-left">
                <h4>Youth Development</h4>
                <p>Lungisa's youth program empowers young people through:</p>
                <br />
                <ul>
                    <li>Life skills training</li>
                    <li>Extra-mural activities including dance and cultural workshops</li>
                    <li>Dialogues on relevant and challenging topics</li>
                    <li>Homework assistance</li>
                </ul>
                <p>These programs offer opportunities to learn new skills, engage in cultural activities, improve academic performance, and develop healthy coping mechanisms</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- ================= BLOCK 4 → COMMUNITY PARTNERSHIP ================= -->
        <article class="service-card">
            <div class="card-body-right">
                <h4>Community Partnerships</h4>
                <p>
                    Lungisa recognizes the importance of collaboration and actively seeks partnerships with:
                    <strong>Community structures • Other non-governmental organizations (NGOs)</strong>.
                    This collaborative approach maximizes impact and fosters sustainable community development.
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/primary-health.jpg" alt="Primary Healthcare">
        </article>

